window/menu/updater/IPC layer have been adapted and rebranded. All original
copyright notices from opencode-electron remain preserved in the source
headers of files that are direct adaptations.

Opencode's workspace packages `@opencode-ai/app` (Solid.js frontend) and
`@opencode-ai/ui` (component kit) are NOT included in Voidex. The Voidex
renderer is written in vanilla TypeScript + CSS, pending a future migration
to void-cli's own React + Ink code-share.
